<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="front-n">front <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /frʌnt/    美 /frʌnt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-the">1.★ <strong>[C] [通常与the连用] 前面；前部；正面：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The front of the postcard shows a picture of the Summer Palace.
明信片的正面是一幅颐和园的照片。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Keep your eyes to the front and walk straight ahead.
眼睛朝前看，一直往前走。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[常用单数] 身体前部：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was lying on her front. 
她俯卧着。</p></div>

<h4 id="3c">3.<strong>[C] [常用单数] 前线；战线；阵线：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Go to the front, young friends!
年轻的朋友们，到前线去吧！</p></div>

<h4 id="4c">4.<strong>[C] (天气) 锋：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a cold / warm front 
冷/暖锋</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-front-of">in front (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在 (…) 前面；在 (…) 面前：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He drove straight into the car in front.
他一下子撞上了前面的车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should be brave in front of difficulties.
我们应该勇敢面对困难。</p><footer>2008 辽宁书面表达</footer></div>

<h3 id="in-the-front-of">in the front (of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在 (…内的) 前部：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The seat in the front is free. 
前面的座位没人坐。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is a big desk for the teacher in the front of the classroom.
教室前面有张大讲桌。</p></div>

<p>注: in front (of) 指在某物外的前面；in the front (of) 指在某物内的前部。  </p></div>